---
import Section from './layout/Section.astro';
import Container from './layout/Container.astro';
import CTAGroup from './layout/CTAGroup.astro';

const schedulingLink = 'https://calendly.com/aldogustavomalasomma/15min';
const briefHref = '/contact#structured-request';
---

<Section variant="plain" class="pb-14 sm:pb-16 lg:pb-20" aria-labelledby="fast-launch-title">
  <Container size="wide">
    <h2 id="fast-launch-title" class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink-900">Fast Launch Engineering</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-slate-700">Launch first. Add automation where it helps. Fix structure before scale.</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Choose the work you need right now.</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Fixed scope, practical implementation, and a clean handoff. No open-ended discovery phase.</p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Compliance-Ready Landing Page</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        A landing page or MVP-style site for startups and digital businesses, built to help you launch fast without creating avoidable GDPR or accessibility issues.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/compliance-ready-landing"
        class="mt-2 inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        aria-label="Explore landing page offer"
      >
        Explore landing page offer
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">From €750</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Typical delivery: 3-5 days</p>
      <div class="mt-3 rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/70 p-3" data-offer-key="tallinn_landing_2026">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900" data-offer="price">Local Launch Offer (Tallinn-based teams): EUR 650</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-emerald-800" data-offer="deadline">Tallinn-based teams · Ends 31 May 2026 (EEST)</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-900" data-offer="slots" aria-live="polite">Slots left: 5</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600" data-offer="active">Available to Tallinn-based teams.</p>
      </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">AI Feature Integration</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Add useful automation when manual workflows start slowing your team down — without overengineering the product.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/ai-feature-integration"
        class="mt-2 inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        aria-label="Explore AI integration offer"
      >
        Explore AI integration offer
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">From €900</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Tactical implementation. Not enterprise AI.</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Typical delivery: 5-7 days</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">EAA Structural Hardening</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Fix structural accessibility issues at code level so your product is easier to use, safer to scale, and closer to EAA/WCAG expectations.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/eaa-structural-hardening"
        class="mt-2 inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        aria-label="Explore accessibility hardening offer"
      >
        Explore accessibility hardening offer
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">From €850</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Typical delivery: 2-4 days</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">System &amp; Compliance Blueprint Sprint</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        A focused review and planning sprint for launch clarity, AI integration direction, and what makes sense to build first.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="mt-2 inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        aria-label="Discuss blueprint sprint"
      >
        Discuss blueprint sprint
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">From €950</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Typical delivery: 7 days</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Need to launch, fix structure, or validate your setup?</h3>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Send a brief or book a short technical assessment. You’ll get clear next steps, a fixed-scope proposal if there’s a fit, and no vague follow-up.
      </p>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        Not ready to reach out yet? Start with the <a href="/guides/" class="font-medium text-brand-700 underline decoration-brand-200 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-800">practical guides</a> on GDPR, EAA, and AI data flow.
      </p>

      <CTAGroup centered class="mt-6">
        <a
          href={schedulingLink}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-soft hover:bg-brand-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        >
          Start with a 15-min Technical Assessment
        </a>
        <a
          href={briefHref}
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        >
          Request a Brief Review
        </a>
      </CTAGroup>

      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-600">No sales pressure. Written follow-up included.</p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
